"status":"completed","activeForm":"Adding version flag to cloche-agent"},{"content":"Add -v/--version to cloched","status":"completed","activeForm":"Adding version flag to cloched"},{"content":"Add -v/--version to cloche CLI (with daemon + agent version lookup)","status":"completed","activeForm":"Adding version flag to cloche CLI"},{"content":"Write tests for version functionality","status":"completed","activeForm":"Writing version tests"},{"content":"Update CLAUDE.md with versioning policy","status":"in_progress","activeForm":"Updating CLAUDE.md"},{"content":"Run go test ./... and fix any failures","status":"pending","activeForm":"Running tests"}],"verificationNudgeNeeded":false}}
