{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Runmd3Mv9wtDN8jUbhYshj","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n**Version package** (`internal/version/`):\n- `VERSION` file containing `0.1.0` — single source of truth\n- `version.go` — reads the version via `go:embed`\n\n**gRPC endpoint**:\n- Added `GetVersion` RPC to `cloche.proto` with `GetVersionRequest`/`GetVersionResponse` messages\n- Regenerated proto code using `buf`\n- Implemented `GetVersion` on `ClocheServer` returning `version.Version()`\n\n**Binary version flags**:\n- `cloche-agent -v` / `--version` — prints agent version\n- `cloched -v` / `--version` — prints daemon version\n- `cloche -v` / `--version` — prints CLI version, queries daemon via gRPC for daemon version, runs `docker run --rm --entrypoint cloche-agent <image> -v` for agent version. Shows `<unavailable>` for unreachable components and warns on version mismatches\n\n**Tests**:\n- `internal/version/version_test.go` — verifies embedded version string\n- `TestServer_GetVersion` in `server_test.go` — verifies gRPC endpoint\n\n**CLAUDE.md** — added versioning policy section covering semver semantics, version commands, and bead ticket policy.\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":415,"cache_read_input_tokens":92615,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":415},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8a8a233a-9bc4-4d5b-81f2-86c5b6995110","uuid":"bd972e0f-609c-436c-bcf2-e71eec9ccb8e"}
